<bibRefCitation author="Speight M. C. D." box="[578,725,900,927]" pageId="4" pageNumber="101" refId="ref5190" refString="Speight M. C. D. 2018. Species accounts of European Syrphidae, 2018. Syrph the Net, the database of European Syrphidae (Diptera), vol. 103, Syrph the Net publications, Dublin, 302 pp." type="book" year="2018">Speight 2018</bibRefCitation>
